summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending page 24-324 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Plat 37W, Page 104 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property located on the west side of 19th Avenue East between East Aloha Street and East Roy Street from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) to Multiple Residence High Density (RMH-350) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of Archdiocese of Seattle 290326) (C.F. 290266).
